      <title>FBI 称去年加密货币欺诈案增长 45%，达到 56 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/crypto-fraud-increased-45-last-year-to-5-6-billion-fbi-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美国联邦调查局的估计，去年消费者因加密货币相关欺诈损失超过 56 亿美元 — — 比 2022 年增长了 45%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/crypto-fraud-increased-45-last-year-to-5-6-billion-fbi-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 19:50:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
